      },
      "date": "2013-04-16 10:28:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI don't understand why Gerrit does not show lines which this patch changes to use tabs instead of spaces for indentation, as it does for other patches, even though the changes _are_ there, and are visible if I 'git fetch' the patch. The reported number of changed lines is +27,-28, but I can only see the few lines that include text changes; Gerrit settings seem to be the same as when viewing other patches. \n\nNot the most important thing in the world, just seems odd; hopefully this is just a one-time glitch of some sort.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
